The special thing about this is that it is a garage door.
"A little bit of engineering went in there," explains Erfan of the steel-reinforced, veneered MDF door.
"It's counterweight so that when you push the door up, it slides very easily."
Thanks to the clever use of space and storage space, Joanne was able to win an additional 16 m2, an additional bedroom and an improved layout.
"At the end of the day, you'll sell the floor space - or how your property is valued," Erfan says.
"In a rudimentary form, a real estate agent will enter and perform a calculation based on the soil size."
