In an interview, Hesemann explains why the final report on the abuse scandal at the Regensburg Domspatzen relieves Georg Ratzinger in his opinion.
Mr. Hesemann, the 440-page report on the "incidents of violence on protective orders at the Regensburg Domspatzen" gives a contradictory picture of cathedral chapel master Georg Ratzinger.
